.card
  .row.align-center
    .small-11.text-center.banner
      %h1 Subprocessors
      %h2= @settings.business_name
  .row.align-center
    .small-11
      .row.align-center
        .small-3.columns
          %h1 Terms
          %a{:href => "/terms/"}
            %p Dashboard Terms
          %a{:href => "/terms/users"}
            %p User Terms
          %a{:href => "/terms/cookies"}
            %p Cookie Policy
          %a{:href => "/terms/gdpr"}
            %p GDPR Compliance
          %a{:href => "/terms/subprocessors"}
            %p Subprocessors &#9668;
          %a{:href => "/terms/privacy"}
            %p Privacy Policy
          %a{:href => "/terms/spam"}
            %p Anti Spam
        .small-9.columns
          %h1 Effective: #{@settings.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y")}
          %p To support delivery of our Services, #{@settings.business_name} may engage and use data processors with access to certain Customer Data (each, a "Subprocessor"). This page provides important information about the identity, location and role of each Subprocessor. Terms used on this page but not defined have the meaning set forth in the Customer Terms of Service or superseding written agreement between Customer and #{@settings.business_name} (the "Agreement").
          %h1 Third Parties
          %p #{@settings.business_name} currently uses third party Subprocessors to provide infrastructure services, and to help us provide customer support and email notifications. Prior to engaging any third party Subprocessor, #{@settings.business_name} performs diligence to evaluate their privacy, security and confidentiality practices, and executes an agreement implementing its applicable obligations.
          %p Since #{@settings.business_name} is a product of Cucumber Tony Limited, all customer & user data is shared and processed by Cucumber Tony Limited.
          %h1 Other Subprocessors
          %p #{@settings.business_name} may use the following Subprocessors to perform other Service functions:
          %ul
            %li Intercom. Cloud-based Customer Support Services. United States
            %li Drift. Cloud-based Customer Support Services. United States
            %li SendGrid. Coud-based Email Notification Services. United States
            %li MailChimp. Coud-based Email Notification Services. United States
            %li Campaign Monitor. Coud-based Email Notification Services. United States
            %li Google Analytics. Website Analytics. United States.
            %li MIMO c/o Cucumber Tony. UK.
          %h3 Contacting #{@settings.business_name}
          %p #{@settings.business_name} #{@settings.business_address}
